<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="dark">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>AI Spectrum & V2V — Dashboard</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/main.css"/>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&family=Rajdhani:wght@300;400;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body>

<!-- TOP NAV -->
<nav class="topnav" id="topnav">
  <div class="nav-brand">
    <span class="brand-icon">📡</span>
    <span class="brand-text">SpectrumAI</span>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-tabs" id="navTabs">
    <button class="nav-tab active" data-page="dataset" onclick="showPage('dataset')">📊 Dataset</button>
    <button class="nav-tab" data-page="orange" onclick="showPage('orange')">🟠 Orange</button>
    <button class="nav-tab" data-page="v2v" onclick="showPage('v2v')">🚗 V2V</button>
    <button class="nav-tab" data-page="ambulance" onclick="showPage('ambulance')">🚑 Ambulance</button>
    <button class="nav-tab" data-page="references" onclick="showPage('references')">📚 References</button>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-controls">
    <span class="admin-badge" id="adminBadge" style="display:none">🔐 Admin</span>
    <label class="theme-toggle">
      <input type="checkbox" id="themeToggle" onchange="toggleTheme()"/>
      <span class="slider">
        <span class="sun">☀️</span>
        <span class="moon">🌙</span>
      </span>
    </label>
    <button class="logout-btn" onclick="doLogout()">⏻</button>
    <button class="ham-btn" id="hamBtn" onclick="toggleMenu()">☰</button>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- WARNING TOAST -->
<div class="warning-toast" id="warningToast"></div>

<!-- PAGES -->
<main class="main-content">

  <!-- ===== DATASET PAGE ===== -->
  <section class="page active" id="page-dataset">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h2 class="page-title">📊 Dataset Extraction</h2>
      <p class="page-sub">Cognitive radio spectrum sensing — raw signal intelligence</p>
      <button class="edit-btn admin-only" onclick="editDataset()" style="display:none">✏ Edit Content</button>
    </div>
    <div class="cards-grid" id="datasetCards">
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🎯</div>
        <h3>Spectrum Frequency Range</h3>
        <ul class="bullet-list" id="freq-list">
          <li>Operating band: <strong>880 MHz – 905 MHz</strong></li>
          <li>Six discrete channels at 5 MHz spacing</li>
          <li>Channels: 880, 885, 890, 895, 900, 905 MHz</li>
          <li>Allocated for V2V DSRC communication</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="card-icon">📶</div>
        <h3>Power & SNR Readings</h3>
        <ul class="bullet-list">
          <li>Power levels: –72 to –102 dBm (measured)</li>
          <li>SNR range: 11 dB to 22 dB per channel</li>
          <li>Higher SNR → Better channel quality</li>
          <li>Free channels identified via energy detection</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🔍</div>
        <h3>Channel Status Classification</h3>
        <ul class="bullet-list">
          <li>Status: OCCUPIED / FREE per channel</li>
          <li>Channels 880, 890, 900 MHz → OCCUPIED</li>
          <li>Channels 885, 895, 905 MHz → FREE</li>
          <li>Dynamic sensing updates every cycle</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🧠</div>
        <h3>AI-Based Decision Logic</h3>
        <ul class="bullet-list">
          <li>Best channel = FREE channel with max SNR</li>
          <li>Backup channel = 2nd best FREE channel</li>
          <li>Collision risk → Switch to backup instantly</li>
          <li>Interference → Redirect through alternate path</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🚗</div>
        <h3>V2V Communication Parameters</h3>
        <ul class="bullet-list">
          <li>Vehicle speed input: 0–120 km/h (adjustable)</li>
          <li>TTC threshold: &lt;2s = High Risk, &lt;4s = Medium</li>
          <li>Closing speed determines collision imminence</li>
          <li>Real-time risk scoring: 0, 0.7, or 1.0</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="card-icon">📡</div>
        <h3>Spectrum Sensing Method</h3>
        <ul class="bullet-list">
          <li>Energy detection on each 5 MHz sub-band</li>
          <li>Threshold-based occupancy classification</li>
          <li>Fast switching (&lt;50ms) for safety-critical data</li>
          <li>Cognitive radio principle: sense → decide → transmit</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Dataset Table -->
    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <h3 class="section-subtitle">📋 Raw Channel Dataset</h3>
    <div class="table-wrap">
      <table class="data-table">
        <thead>
          <tr><th>#</th><th>Frequency (MHz)</th><th>Power (dBm)</th><th>SNR (dB)</th><th>Status</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>1</td><td>880</td><td>–72</td><td>22</td><td><span class="badge-occ">OCCUPIED</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td>2</td><td>885</td><td>–95</td><td>14</td><td><span class="badge-free">FREE</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td>3</td><td>890</td><td>–78</td><td>18</td><td><span class="badge-occ">OCCUPIED</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td>4</td><td>895</td><td>–102</td><td>11</td><td><span class="badge-free">FREE</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td>5</td><td>900</td><td>–75</td><td>20</td><td><span class="badge-occ">OCCUPIED</span></td></tr>
          <tr><td>6</td><td>905</td><td>–98</td><td>12</td><td><span class="badge-free">FREE</span></td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== ORANGE PAGE ===== -->
  <section class="page" id="page-orange">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h2 class="page-title">🟠 Orange — Data Mining</h2>
      <p class="page-sub">Visual intelligence from spectrum and traffic datasets</p>
      <button class="edit-btn admin-only" id="addOrangeBtn" onclick="addOrangeItem()" style="display:none">＋ Add Item</button>
    </div>
    <div class="orange-grid" id="orangeGrid">
      <!-- Items injected by JS -->
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== V2V PAGE ===== -->
  <section class="page" id="page-v2v">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h2 class="page-title">🚗 V2V Communication System</h2>
      <p class="page-sub">Time-To-Collision logic with intelligent channel switching</p>
    </div>

    <!-- V2V Simulation -->
    <div class="sim-container">
      <div class="sim-card road-card">
        <h3>🛣 Live Road Simulation</h3>
        <canvas id="roadCanvas" width="400" height="300"></canvas>
        <div class="sim-controls">
          <label>Bus Speed: <span id="busVal">80</span> km/h</label>
          <input type="range" id="busSlider" min="0" max="120" value="80" oninput="updateSim()"/>
          <label>Bike Speed: <span id="bikeVal">40</span> km/h</label>
          <input type="range" id="bikeSlider" min="0" max="120" value="40" oninput="updateSim()"/>
          <button class="sim-btn" id="v2vPlayBtn" onclick="toggleV2V()">▶ Start</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sim-card channel-card">
        <h3>📡 Channel Status</h3>
        <canvas id="channelCanvas" width="350" height="200"></canvas>
        <div class="channel-legend">
          <span class="leg active-ch">● Active</span>
          <span class="leg free-ch">● Free</span>
          <span class="leg occ-ch">● Occupied</span>
        </div>
        <div class="status-box" id="v2vStatus">System initializing…</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="graph-row">
      <div class="graph-card">
        <h4>Speed vs Time</h4>
        <canvas id="speedChart" width="400" height="200"></canvas>
      </div>
      <div class="graph-card">
        <h4>Collision Risk vs Time</h4>
        <canvas id="riskChart" width="400" height="200"></canvas>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- MATLAB Code -->
    <div class="code-section">
      <h3>💻 MATLAB Source Code — V2V TTC Logic</h3>
      <div class="code-block" id="v2vCode"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <h3 class="section-subtitle">📌 How It Works</h3>
    <div class="cards-grid small-cards">
      <div class="info-card"><div class="card-icon">⏱</div><h3>TTC Calculation</h3><p>Time-To-Collision = Distance ÷ Closing Speed. If TTC &lt; 2s, collision risk = 1.0 (critical).</p></div>
      <div class="info-card"><div class="card-icon">📻</div><h3>Channel Switching</h3><p>On collision detection, system instantly switches from primary to backup channel for emergency braking data.</p></div>
      <div class="info-card"><div class="card-icon">⚡</div><h3>Interference Handling</h3><p>When ego and front vehicle speeds are nearly equal (&lt;0.5 m/s difference), interference is detected and backup channel is used.</p></div>
      <div class="info-card"><div class="card-icon">✅</div><h3>Normal Operation</h3><p>Best FREE channel (highest SNR) used for routine V2V telemetry. System continuously monitors all 6 channels.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== AMBULANCE PAGE ===== -->
  <section class="page" id="page-ambulance">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h2 class="page-title">🚑 Ambulance Priority System</h2>
      <p class="page-sub">Emergency vehicle clearance via V2V spectrum communication</p>
    </div>

    <div class="sim-container">
      <div class="sim-card road-card">
        <h3>🚑 3D Traffic Simulation</h3>
        <canvas id="ambCanvas" width="400" height="300"></canvas>
        <div class="sim-controls">
          <label>Ambulance Speed: <span id="ambVal">15</span> m/s</label>
          <input type="range" id="ambSlider" min="5" max="30" value="15" oninput="updateAmb()"/>
          <label>Vehicle Speed: <span id="vehVal">10</span> m/s</label>
          <input type="range" id="vehSlider" min="5" max="25" value="10" oninput="updateAmb()"/>
          <button class="sim-btn" id="ambPlayBtn" onclick="toggleAmb()">▶ Start</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sim-card channel-card">
        <h3>🚨 Emergency Status</h3>
        <div class="emergency-panel" id="emergencyPanel">
          <div class="emg-item" id="ambMsg">
            <span class="emg-icon">🚑</span>
            <span id="ambMsgText">Proceed Normally</span>
          </div>
          <div class="emg-item" id="vehMsg">
            <span class="emg-icon">🚗</span>
            <span id="vehMsgText">Maintain Lane</span>
          </div>
          <div class="emg-item" id="chMsg">
            <span class="emg-icon">📡</span>
            <span id="chMsgText">Using Primary (885 MHz)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="risk-meter">
            <label>Risk Level</label>
            <div class="meter-bar"><div class="meter-fill" id="riskFill" style="width:0%"></div></div>
            <span id="riskPct">0%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="graph-row">
      <div class="graph-card">
        <h4>Speed Comparison</h4>
        <canvas id="ambSpeedChart" width="400" height="200"></canvas>
      </div>
      <div class="graph-card">
        <h4>Emergency Risk Level</h4>
        <canvas id="ambRiskChart" width="400" height="200"></canvas>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="code-section">
      <h3>💻 MATLAB Source Code — Ambulance Priority</h3>
      <div class="code-block" id="ambCode"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <h3 class="section-subtitle">📌 Emergency Logic Explained</h3>
    <div class="cards-grid small-cards">
      <div class="info-card"><div class="card-icon">🚨</div><h3>Priority Clearance</h3><p>Ambulance detected as primary vehicle. All civilian vehicles receive V2V signals to yield immediately.</p></div>
      <div class="info-card"><div class="card-icon">📻</div><h3>Dedicated Channel</h3><p>Emergency V2V uses backup channel to avoid interference with normal traffic, ensuring reliable delivery.</p></div>
      <div class="info-card"><div class="card-icon">⬅</div><h3>Lane Override</h3><p>TTC &lt; 2s triggers "Move LEFT Immediately" command broadcast to civilian vehicle via V2X protocol.</p></div>
      <div class="info-card"><div class="card-icon">🌐</div><h3>3D Visualization</h3><p>Real-time 3D road simulation shows ambulance and civilian vehicle positions, speeds, and clearance status.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== REFERENCES PAGE ===== -->
  <section class="page" id="page-references">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h2 class="page-title">📚 References</h2>
      <p class="page-sub">Research papers, standards, and prior art</p>
      <button class="edit-btn admin-only" id="addRefBtn" onclick="addReference()" style="display:none">＋ Add Reference</button>
    </div>
    <div class="ref-grid" id="refGrid">
      <!-- Injected by JS -->
    </div>
  </section>

</main>

<!-- ADMIN MODAL -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="modalOverlay" onclick="closeModal()"></div>
<div class="modal" id="adminModal">
  <div class="modal-header">
    <h3 id="modalTitle">Edit Content</h3>
    <button onclick="closeModal()">✕</button>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-body" id="modalBody"></div>
  <div class="modal-footer">
    <button class="btn-save" onclick="saveModal()">💾 Save</button>
    <button class="btn-cancel" onclick="closeModal()">Cancel</button>
  </div>
</div>

<script src="js/data.js"></script>
<script src="js/simulation.js"></script>
<script src="js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
